headline: Is Mastercard a Millionaire Maker?
summary: Mastercard shares the limelight with Visa, but is it the best stock to buy if you're looking to build a seven-figure nest egg?

headline: Where Will Visa Stock Be in 3 Years?
summary: This might be an opportune time to buy Visa (NYSE: V) stock.  The credit card giant is an all-weather stock because it does well when the economy does, which is most of the time.  The market continues to hit new highs since the election, and that bodes well for Visa and its shareholders.
